WELCOME.TITLE: Welcome
WELCOME.VALID-FLEET: Check and approve a Fleet Manager that performed the self-registration procedure.
WELCOME.VALID-VEHICLE: Check and approve vehicles inserted by Fleet Manager.
WELCOME.VEHICLE: View main and statistichal data of your vehicles. Assign a driver to a vehicle.
WELCOME.VEHICLE-DRIVER: View main data of your vehicles. Select your vehicles.
WELCOME.FLEET-MANAGER: Insert a new Fleet Manager user or change dat of an existing Fleet Manager.
WELCOME.ADD-OBU: Assign an OBU to a vehicle belonging to a Fleet Manager; bail was previously paid
WELCOME.ADD-TICKET: Assign a Ticket sold by SaS to a vehicle belonging to a Fleet Manager with installed OBU.
WELCOME.MANAGE-TICKET: Manage Tickets sold by SaS assigned to your vehicles.
WELCOME.Test: Check the inspection documents of vehicles. Perform the inspection procedure on an installed OBU.
WELCOME.APPOINTMENTS: Insert a new appointment to install an OBU. View main data of Fleet Manager owning the vehicles on which OBUs should be installed.
